{
  "texts": [
    "In the high-tech or voice assistant field, DSR is applied to dialect speech search and intelligent customer service.",
    "Through dialect speech search (Chiang 2017), users can find the required information faster and improve the experience.",
    "By using dialect intelligent customer service, users can communicate with enterprises more conveniently, which improves service quality and efficiency.",
    "For example, Chinese dialect voice commands are used to operate mobile applications (Ma 2014) and handle related business, etc.",
    "DSR is also widely used in the court system to improve work efficiency and serve the public better."
  ]
}